rows.label: tev041201_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev041201_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Nauzo about his work.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev041201_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Nauzo if anything is troubling him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0001
rows.name: I work at this plant. Ma-non used to be scared of me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0002
rows.name:
But I did my work. They did theirs.
Soon they learn I am not bad like Cavern Clan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0003
rows.name:
Now we talk. Or they talk. I mostly listen.
Ma-non have many interesting things to say.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0004
rows.name: Other day, they let me try pizza. It was not bad.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0008
rows.name: This is my job. I use machines to destroy garbage.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0009
rows.name:
Machines are complicated. Many moving parts.
I still have much to learn.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0010
rows.name:
Sometimes there are problems.
Then red lamp on machine goes "Beep, beep."
I do not like problems.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0011
rows.name:
Swift kick stops beeping. Problem goes away.
But I worry I might break machine one day.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_SEL1011
rows.name: Ask Nauzo about humans.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Nauzo about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Nauzo about recycling.

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0012
rows.name:
Earth aliens like making things.
But like throwing them away more![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0013
rows.name:
Prone use every part of beast. Especially bones.
They make good plate. Solid armor.
No need to throw them away![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0014
rows.name:
Integrated production plant does that.
They "re-cicle" waste from my job.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0015
rows.name: Won't Mira run out of resources soon?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0018
rows.name:
Liza hired Zaruboggan. She is great chieftain!
So smart to hire them![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0019
rows.name: I would follow smart chieftain like her to end of Mira.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0020
rows.name:
So now we are ready!
We will get rid of all garbage in NLA![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0021
rows.name: No more kicking machines. No more beeping.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0027
rows.name:
Some waste is recycled. But not all.
Do you know why?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0028
rows.name:
Some say it is because Mira's resources are strange.
We do not understand them yet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0029
rows.name: Simpler to incinerate them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0030
rows.name:
I do not understand this.
Why do Earth aliens burn valuable resources?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Nauzo about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0022
rows.name:
The more I hit machine, the more smoke came out.
I thought I was fired for sure.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0023
rows.name:
Good thing Zaruboggan came along!
I was very lucky.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0024
rows.name:
Well, mostly Chieftain Liza was lucky.
Her luck is special. I should stick by her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0025
rows.name: If I ever get in more trouble, her luck will save me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041201_MSG0026
rows.name: Then I can kick machine as much as I want![ST:wait ]
